These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-1::.
6 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, hamster, horse, pony, rabbit, snake
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, daisy, poppy, begonia, aconite, tulip
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the owner of the pony is the person who growstulip##1
3. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the person who growstulip and the person who growsaconite##2
5. the person who growsaconite is in an even position##4
6. the person who growsdaisy is on the far right##1
7. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3
8. the owner of the snake is the person who growspoppy##1
9. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2   |     3      |  4   |     5      |    6    |
| Pet         | rabbit     | horse | guinea-pig | pony | snake      | hamster |
| Flower   | begonia | aconite  | balloon-flower    | tulip | poppy | daisy    |

