.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-2::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, pall-mall, davidoff, blend, bluemaster, alhambra
There are 6 different nationalities: brazilian, british, chinese, dutch, italian, japanese
 1. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the brazilian##1
 2. the dutch is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the brazilian##1
 4. the japanese is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 5. the davidoff-smoker is the dutch##1
 6. the havana-smoker is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
 7. the chinese is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the italian is in an even position##4
 9. the havana-smoker is on the left of the italian##1
10. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the bluemaster-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |      5      |    6    |
| Cigar   | havana  | blend  | bluemaster | pall-mall   | alhambra | davidoff |
| Nationality   | chinese | italian | british    | japanese | brazilian   | dutch   |

