.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-3::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, baccarat, ritmeester, montecristo, swisher, blend
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: basketball, cycling, golf, handball, ice-hockey, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the ritmeester-smoker##3
4. the montecristo-smoker is in an odd position##4
5. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the montecristo-smoker##3
6. the swisher-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
7. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
8. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left or far right##3
9. the person who's sport is handball is the blend-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |    3    |       4       |     5      |    6     |
| Cigar   | dunhill    | swisher | ritmeester     | baccarat         | montecristo       | blend     |
| Sport         | basketball | golf  | cycling | weightlifting | ice-hockey | handball |

