.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: action, drama, family, satire, scientific, superhero
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, prince, bongani, chaman, tiparillo, dunhill
1. the alhambra-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the chaman-smoker##3
3. the person watching action movies is on the far left##1
4. the chaman-smoker is in an even position##4
5. the bongani-smoker is the person watching family movies##1
6. the prince-smoker is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3
7. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
8. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
9. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| Movie-Genre   | action | drama     | family     | satire | scientific | superhero |
| Cigar     | dunhill    | prince | bongani | chaman  | tiparillo       | alhambra      |

