 6. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
 7. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
 8. the owner of the turtle is the russian##1
 9. the owner of the horse is on the far left or far right##3
10. the turkish is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6    |
