.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-7::.
City: san-francisco, prague, london, edinburgh, marseilles, paris
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: badminton, cricket, lacrosse, rugby, snowboarding, tennis
 1. the person who's sport is tennis is the person traveling to paris##1
 2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person traveling to edinburgh##3
 3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
 4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
 6. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
 7. the person traveling to prague is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
 8. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 9. the person traveling to san-francisco is in an even position##4
10. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |        1        |      2       |         3          |    4     |     5     |   6    |
| City     | edinburgh | prague     | marseilles | san-francisco  | london     | paris |
| Sport   | cricket         | snowboarding | rugby              | lacrosse | badminton | tennis |

