.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-8::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: skydiving, rock-climbing, fishing, filmmaking, drawing, gardening
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: cricket, snowboarding, surfing, swimming, volleyball, weightlifting
 1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
 3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 6. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 7. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
10. the person who's sport is cricket is in an odd position##4
11. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far right##1
12. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2     |    3     |       4       |     5      |      6       |
| Hobby   | skydiving | fishing     | rock-climbing | gardening         | drawing        | filmmaking       |
| Sport      | surfing       | swimming | cricket  | weightlifting | volleyball | snowboarding |

