.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-9::.
House: art-deco, gothic-revival, futuristic, tower, modern, ranch-style
The people have 6 different hobbies: filmmaking, hiking, magic-tricks, puzzles, skydiving, writing
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is the tower house##1
3. the tower house is on the right of the modern house##1
4. the modern house is in an even position##4
5. the person who's hobby is writing is between the futuristic house and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far right##1
7. the modern house is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
8. the ranch-style house is on the far left##1

