.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-10::.
6 different pets are kept: pony, lizard, hedgehog, rabbit, frog, dog
The people use 6 different means of transport: motorbike, quad-bike, scooter, ship, train, van
 1. the person driving the ship is between the owner of the hedgehog and the owner of the frog##2
 2. the person driving the train is on the far left##1
 3. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 4. the owner of the dog is the person driving the ship##1
 5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
 6. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is the owner of the lizard##1
 8. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
 9. the owner of the pony is the person driving the train##1
10. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
11. the owner of the pony is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |       3       |   4   |     5     |    6    |
| Pet    | pony | rabbit | hedgehog | dog | frog      | lizard    |
| Transport   | train       | van      | quad-bike     | ship  | motorbike | scooter |

