 3. the person playing chess is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 4. the person driving the taxi is between the person driving the airplane and the person driving the quad-bike##2
 5. the person playing chess is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 7. the person driving the quad-bike is in an even position##4
 8. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 9. the person driving the airplane is the person playing backgammon##1
10. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1

