.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-20::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: blood-red, yellow, turquise, black, ebony, light-blue
The people have 6 different jobs:  doctor, firefighter, freelancer, lawyer, paramedic, security-guard
 1. the lawyer is on the left or right of the person who likes light-blue##3
 2. the person who likes ebony is in an even position##4
 3. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
 4. the person who likes yellow is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
 5. the security-guard is on the right of the lawyer##1
 6. the person who likes blood-red is the paramedic##1
 7. the person who likes turquise is in an even position##4
 8. the freelancer is on the far right##1
 9. the doctor is between the person who likes ebony and the firefighter##2
10. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
11. the person who likes yellow is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
12. the lawyer is on the right of the doctor##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |      2      |   3    |   4    |       5        |     6      |
| Color   | blood-red    | turquise      | black  | ebony  | light-blue           | yellow  |
| Job    | paramedic | firefighter | doctor | lawyer | security-guard | freelancer |

 